<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//Apache Software Foundation//DTD XDOC 1.0//EN" "http://maven.apache.org/dtd/xdoc_1_0.dtd">
<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Hippo Utilities Release Notes</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="Release Notes">
      <subsection name="1.02.00">
        <ul>
          <li>HIPPLUG-836: Upgrade to 7.9.</li>
          <li>Remove <a href="repository/scheduler-daemon.html">Scheduler Daemon</a>: similar functionality is
            <a href="http://www.onehippo.org/library/concepts/hippo-services/repository-scheduler.html">now available in Hippo Repository</a>.</li>
          <li>Remove Gallery Processor: the functionality is now available in Hippo CMS core.</li>
          <li>Upgrade and clean up dependencies.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.01.02">
        <ul>
          <li>HIPPLUG-338: skip terracotta autoupdate by setting a property in the Scheduler Daemon</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.01.01">
        <ul>
          <li>Scheduler Daemon: added a mandatory properties file with activation flag
            'org.onehippo.forge.utilities.repository.scheduler.SchedulerDaemon.active', on behalf of clustered setup</li>
          <li>Scheduler Daemon: added BaseJob class providing access to JCR session and job configuration</li>
          <li>NodeUtils: moved from repository module (scheduler) to commons module</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.01.00">
        <ul>
          <li>Initial release as a restructured version of PSUtils forge project,
            <a href="http://psutils.forge.onehippo.org/release-notes.html">see PSUtils release notes</a></li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>
